@duststorm_to_filters
title: I understand the problem better. Let me test a possible action.
go-to: 27_fq_cause_effect

Me: I understand the problem better. Let me test a possible action.

Ranger Neral gathers the stems back into the cloth, but a black smear of ash remains on the table between you.

Facilyn: Good. Hold your preferred action lightly for a moment.

Facilyn: First we ask the most important opening question: does it address the root cause, or only the dust in the air?

